    • data.problem.ProblemInputs

  • public class ProblemInputs
extends java.lang.Object
    ProblemInputs will contain the inputs for the problem. It will be the most important class that each @see JMetalWorker will work with. This class contains all the information necessary for the algorithms to run, including lists rules and restrictions.
